Hotkeys on Microsoft Word

***************************

Switch Programs:
Alt+Tab

Create a new document:
Ctrl+N

Open a document:
Ctrl+O

Save the document:
Ctrl+S

Close the document:
Ctrl+W

Copy text:
Ctrl+C

Paste text:
Ctrl+V

Cut text:
Ctrl+X

Select all text:
Ctrl+A

Bold formatting:
Ctrl+B

Italics formatting:
Ctrl+I

Underline text:
Ctrl+U

Decrease the font size by 1 point:
Ctrl+Left bracket ([)

Increase the font size by 1 point:
Ctrl+Right bracket (])

Center text:
Ctrl+E

Align the text to the left:
Ctrl+L

Align the text to the right:
Ctrl+R

Undo the previous action:
Ctrl+Z

Redo the previous action, if possible:
Ctrl+Y

Split the document window and remove split:
Ctrl+Alt+S
